revision.text:
{{Documentation subpage}}
{{High-use}}

== Usage ==
Use this template to provide the [[Royal Thai General System of Transcription]] romanization of Thai words and phrases.

* {{tlc|RTGS|transcribed text}}

==Parameters==
* The parameter {{para|link|no}} may be specified to disable the link.
* The parameter {{para|italic|yes}} or {{para|italic|no}} may be used to specify whether the text should be italicized. Defaults to {{para|italic|}}, which italicizes the output.
* To specify text as being an RTGS transcription without displaying the label "RTGS", use {{tl|tlit}} directly, as such:
*: {{tlc|tlit|th|RTGS|transcribed text}}

<includeonly>{{sandbox other||
